src.rpm is available from download section:
 https://github.com/downloads/bookwar/lxpanelx-rpm/lxpanelx-0.5.6-1.svn146.src.rpm

Package conflicts with original lxpanel package.

First rebuild

$ rpmbuild --rebuild lxpanelx-0.5.6-1.svn146.src.rpm

then install

$ yum shell
 > remove lxpanel
 > install lxpanelx-0.5.6-1.svn146.<smth>.rpm
 > run

Check that lxde-common has not been uninstalled.

Then relogin into LXDE.